项目运行结果[FAILURE] [WS-CLEANUP] Deleting project workspace... [WS-CLEANUP] Deferred wipeout is used... [WS-CLEANUP] done Finished: FAILURE"}]},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"原因很清楚 —— 跟代码没关系，是 M4pro 这台 Mac 构建节点上 Xcode license 没同意。\n\n关键报错：\n\n> `You have not agreed to the Xcode license agreements. Please run 'sudo xcodebuild -license' from within a Terminal window to review and agree to the Xcode and Apple SDKs license.`\n\n`git init` 返回了 exit code 69，macOS 上的 git 依赖 Xcode Command Line Tools，Xcode 更新后需要重新同意 license，不然所有 git 命令都会被拦住。\n\nSSH 到 M4pro 那台机器上执行：\n\n```bash\nsudo xcodebuild -license accept\n```\n\n跑完之后重新触发构建就行了。如果这台机器你没 sudo 权限，找运维帮忙跑一下这条命令。"}]},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-06 02:30 UTC] 你还记得昨天让你写的那个openclaw+aiclient的md文档和html吧 md文档需要更新 把以下部分 作为一个建议章节补充上去，然后也补充到html中。注意好结构编号。 ## 背景 之前 AIClient-2-API 是在 Kiro 终端里通过 `npm start` 运行的，Kiro 升级/重启会导致进程被杀。为了保证服务持续运行，将 AIClient 和 OpenClaw 一起放进 Docker 管理。 ## docker-compose 配置 文件路径: `docker/docker-compose.openclaw.yml` 核心思路： - aiclient 容器挂载本地项目目录 (`..:/app`)，用 `node:20-alpine` 运行 - openclaw 使用 `network_mode: \"service:aiclient\"` 共享 aiclient 的网络命名空间，这样 openclaw 内部访问 `localhost:3000` 就能直接到达 aiclient - openclaw 的对外端口 (18789) 必须声明在 aiclient 的 `ports` 中（因为共享网络命名空间后 openclaw 自己不能声明端口） ```bash # 启动 cd docker docker compose -f docker-compose.openclaw.yml up -d # 停止 docker compose -f docker-compose.openclaw.yml down ``` ## 切换到 Docker 后的已知问题 ### 1. 重启 aiclient 必须同时重启 openclaw `network_mode: \"service:aiclient\"` 意味着 openclaw 绑定到 aiclient 容器的网络命名空间。如果只重启 aiclient，容器 ID 变化导致网络命名空间断开，openclaw 内部 `localhost:3000` 不通。 ```bash # 正确做法：一起重启 docker restart docker-aiclient-1 docker-openclaw-1 ``` ### 2. OpenClaw 发送 `/chat/completions` 而非 `/v1/chat/completions` OpenClaw 忽略 `BASE_URL` 中的路径部分，实际请求路径是 `POST /chat/completions`（没有 `/v1` 前缀）。AIClient 的路由只匹配 `/v1/chat/completions`，导致 404。 修复位置: `src/services/api-manager.js` ```javascript // 原始 if (path === '/v1/chat/completions') { // 改为 if (path === '/v1/chat/completions' || path === '/chat/completions') { ``` ### 3. Web UI 自动更新会覆盖代码修改 AIClient 的 Web UI 有在线更新功能，更新时会用 tarball 覆盖整个 `src` 目录。这意味着上面第 2 点的路由别名修改会丢失。 更新后如果 OpenClaw 又报 404，重新加上 `/chat/completions` 路由别名即可。"}]},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nLet me find the existing documents first."}],"tool_calls":[{"id":"tooluse_SElLklMbHIhCzg4GxQQgKN","type":"function","function":{"name":"exec","arguments":"{\"command\":\"find /home/node/.openclaw/workspace -name \\\"OpenClaw-AIClient*\\\" -type f 2>/dev/null\"}"}},{"id":"tooluse_EU0QMJwYADC2cSbLuLHmkZ","type":"function","function":{"name":"nodes","arguments":"{\"action\":\"run\",\"node\":\"CNMCYF4744KJ\",\"command\":[\"find\",\"/Users/kidd/.openclaw/workspace\",\"-name\",\"OpenClaw-AIClient*\",\"-type\",\"f\"]}"}}]},{"role":"tool","content":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/docs/OpenClaw-AIClient-Setup-Guide.md\n/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/docs/OpenClaw-AIClient-Setup-Guide.html","tool_call_id":"tooluse_SElLklMbHIhCzg4GxQQgKN"},{"role":"tool","content":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"nodes\",\n  \"error\": \"agent=main node=CNMCYF4744KJ gateway=default action=run: system.run requires a companion app or node host; the selected node does not support system.run.\"\n}","tool_call_id":"tooluse_EU0QMJwYADC2cSbLuLHmkZ"}],"stream":true,"stream_options":{"include_usage":true},"store":false,"max_completion_tokens":8192,"tools":[{"type":"function","function":{"name":"read","description":"Read the contents of a file. Supports text files and images (jpg, png, gif, webp). Images are sent as attachments. For text files, output is truncated to 2000 lines or 50KB (whichever is hit first). Use offset/limit for large files. When you need the full file, continue with offset until complete.","parameters":{"type":"object","required":[],"properties":{"path":{"description":"Path to the file to read (relative or absolute)","type":"string"},"offset":{"description":"Line number to start reading 