 GIF 生成 MCP\n\n## cron 任务问题排查\n- 中东局势日报 cron 首次执行报 403，手动重跑成功。403 原因不明确，可能是 cron 首次执行时 session 初始化问题或瞬时网络问题。input_tokens=15945 但 output_tokens=0，说明 prompt 送到了但模型没返回。重跑后正常（耗时199秒，成功投递）。后续观察是否复现。\n"}]},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"tooluse_HVrkRPd2hpjZoeEHmBQwqT","name":"web_fetch","input":{"url":"http://10.126.9.183:8080/job/EP/150/console"}}]},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"tooluse_HVrkRPd2hpjZoeEHmBQwqT","content":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"web_fetch\",\n  \"error\": \"Blocked hostname or private/internal/special-use IP address\"\n}"}]},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这个 Jenkins 地址是内网的（10.126.x.x），我从这边没法直接访问。\n\n你可以试试这几个方式让我帮你看：\n\n1. 直接把构建日志的报错部分复制粘贴给我\n2. 或者截图发过来，我帮你分析\n\n哪种方便就来哪种 🐕"}]},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-06 02:26 UTC] 日志如下： Started by remote host 10.126.112.90 Running as SYSTEM [EnvInject] - Loading node environment variables. Building remotely on M4pro (Mpro) in workspace /Users/mccldp/jenkins/workspace/EP [WS-CLEANUP] Deleting project workspace... [WS-CLEANUP] Deferred wipeout is used... The recommended git tool is: NONE using credential mac Cloning the remote Git repository Cloning repository https://gitlab-ex.mcd.com.cn/store-operation/e-production/epro-boss-subapp > git init /Users/mccldp/jenkins/workspace/EP # timeout=10 ERROR: Error cloning remote repo 'origin' hudson.plugins.git.GitException: Could not init /Users/mccldp/jenkins/workspace/EP at PluginClassLoader for git-client//org.jenkinsci.plugins.gitclient.CliGitAPIImpl$5.execute(CliGitAPIImpl.java:1082) at PluginClassLoader for git-client//org.jenkinsci.plugins.gitclient.CliGitAPIImpl$2.execute(CliGitAPIImpl.java:828) at PluginClassLoader for git-client//org.jenkinsci.plugins.gitclient.RemoteGitImpl$CommandInvocationHandler$GitCommandMasterToSlaveCallable.call(RemoteGitImpl.java:173) at PluginClassLoader for git-client//org.jenkinsci.plugins.gitclient.RemoteGitIm